Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已经完全搞不清自己的方位了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别吓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这前面有隐藏的阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是这儿的略图么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎么搞到手的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚刚有人用箭书给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那之前的阶梯也是她搞的鬼么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是究竟是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:02.49,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\bord2\blur5\1a&HFF\3c&H5A5760&\pos(957,550)}超秘传忍法书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:02.49,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\c&HE3EFED&\pos(957,550)}超秘传忍法书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没错 都向秘传书靠拢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是你所期望的事么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看你好像挺担心学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是来见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是我的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在我任务失败 濒临死亡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我领悟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真正的强大正在于“恶”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想要证明这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}通过战胜你所培养的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你几次佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是想锻炼我们这的姑娘们么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在极短的时间内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的学生以令人惊异的速度成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不愧是你啊 雾夜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:04:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}令被超秘传忍法书选中的少女们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后当我的学生胜出的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我应该就能成为夙愿的超级忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阳之秘传忍法书在这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说 夺走秘传书的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被利益私欲蒙住双眼校主道元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}独断专行让学生做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}让阴阳结合是忍者最大的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然这过程不是出于我的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但这下也能做个了断了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我与你的学生之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}终会有人继承秘传忍法书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后对决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是小孩子的口角么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在得出结果前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就在这里和我一起观赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾夜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彷徨到头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如此再会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}实属讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你曾是我可爱的学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还想要胜过我么
