Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:06:01.04,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}庞若螺旋 赤罠笼络
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:08.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}铭刻现实 掷向彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:14.05,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}远空迢遥 一瞬閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}绮丽绽放 犹纏暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:19.35,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}耀于朧云上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}所坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:27.53,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}誓以我手 开辟我路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:32.53,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}击穿那道 无形枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:35.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}无须悲伤与苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.92,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}谁能正确的去解读未来? 只有你自己知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:40.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}准备好! 辨别是非
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:42.32,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}打破你的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:49.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}「保有自尊」与「守护家园」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}一直以来 都没发觉到其中意义的差别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}我行我素地妄自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:07:00.08,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}谁的背上承载着 正在飞翔的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}如同祈愿般 疏远的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:05.23,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}过去细碎微小的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:10.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}世俗的浪涛 如此寂静又虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:17.73,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}将怜悯给焚烧殆尽 斩破虚无幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:23.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}正直的双瞳 閃出强烈的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.19,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}来吧 群起乱舞 委身寄于时空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}在这崇敬的天空解放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.28,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}唯独意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:36.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}在此身腐朽走到尽头之前决不就此停步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:42.79,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}在这永恒的梦境里 借由烈焰指引
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:07.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}无法停下脚步 朝向欢笑满载的居所...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:15.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}在这混沌的日常 灵魂交错重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:21.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}远空迢遥 一瞬閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:24.07,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}绮丽绽放 犹纏暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.53,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}耀于朧云上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.24,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}所坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:34.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}誓以我手 开辟我路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:39.94,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}击穿那道 无形枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:42.32,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}无须悲伤与苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:45.05,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}谁能正确的去解读未来? 只有你自己知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:47.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}准备好! 辨别是非
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.81,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}打破你的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}此战胜不在吾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而在吾之学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最高层就在这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不会让你们逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们输了不就会死么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么还这么冷静！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们会死 跟汝有什么关系么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但咱家就是不爽这做法！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真搞不懂汝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}问题不在你搞不搞得懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而是咱家爽不爽！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算拼上蛮力咱家也要闯过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看到这眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知怎的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像有另一个我要探出头来一般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是带着感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么能做战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你竟敢像这样暴露感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向我攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼 突然发什么火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}搞不懂搞不懂搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样的你也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有个人样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾夜老师亲传！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真够古风的一招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道她们要往哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这回绝不会放过她们！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我羡慕这份家族爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咏同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还是头一次看见日影这么有干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已经放弃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不多反抗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我蹂躏你也没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}柳生 忍舞参上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼 果然来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把云雀还给俺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她是要当我人偶的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不会放过你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊呀 未来你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下来才是好戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可不能让春花姐一个人独享啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都说了现在不是做这些事情的时候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H989EF4&}秘传忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H989EF4&}兔子先生 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H989EF4&}冲散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}合体秘传忍法么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那种事情有可能么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所谓忍术 即为心技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}铃音老师常这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}亲密无间到了可以化不可能为可能的程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这也许…也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要追咯 未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小焰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你还真是天真到家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你以为只有一条路么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H0500C6&}秘传忍法“魁”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H67A63C&}秘传忍法“二刀缭斩”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼 战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消磨性命相斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被选中的两个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小焰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种战斗毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被选中的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道元大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被选中的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个人就是云雀说过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}焰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与那女孩一同来到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}随着这超秘传忍法书的指引一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和飞鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道元大人 这究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了将你们这些被选中的人作为根据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}令超秘传忍法书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阴之卷 阳之卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这两股力量纳入我手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那种事情是绝不能允许的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可不能反抗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本来这所谓的蛇女子学园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不过是我野心的垫脚石罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我将用这力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}将恶忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 是超越所有忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你打算背叛组织么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道元大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道元他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了自己的私欲 背叛了我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有恶忍组织
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然感觉有点乱糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目标是道元咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 做好觉悟吧 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小飞鸟和焰同学不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被关进结界里了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们已经落入我手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就展示给你们看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的秘传忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}“大蛇”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur5\pos(640,650)}致天国的怨楼血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这些家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他们不是普通的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而是用来守卫的机关忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:12:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}机关！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人家才不是想来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毕竟现在该对战的敌人不是我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}挺厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然一点也不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你先保存体力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有别的事等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抵抗我的“大蛇”毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你竟敢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如此…利用我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可笑至极
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是因为你的愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小焰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}利用 还是被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都取决于自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}若这就是我的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以恶之宿命 殉舞参上！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}让我带你上路吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以轻易丢掉性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我这条命本就是给恶忍捡回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事到如今 一条性命有啥好可惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同伴们一定会来救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}相信同伴们吧 小焰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这下全都收拾完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剩下的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那结界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是由阴阳两卷超秘传忍法书所铸起的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要比我所建的联动结界坚固许多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但若集合我们全员的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你以前曾经突破过我们的联动结界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那时能够进入结界 并非是靠俺的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而是托了云雀的福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫你先留存体力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要将大家的心绪传达给她们两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这一定会成为一股巨大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}巨大的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}利用不同的结界间的相位差
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使其它变得不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真没想到会和你们联手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咏同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胜负只能延期了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}焰同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小焰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小飞鸟 焰同学 快听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听听大家的声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要是倒下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么有脸回去见她们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:25.79,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:26.43,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:27.89,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小飞鸟 焰同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼唤大家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感受大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家是想来救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同伴们？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}区区忍者学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:16:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家在我心里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}激烈 而又温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊 这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家的思念化为了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她们想要守护我的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刀和盾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明白了 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}秘传书！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H0500C6&}超·秘传忍法“红”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\blur8\3c&H67A63C&}超·秘传忍法“半藏流乱咲”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:47.94,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\s1}#我家小焰竟然只有这么两秒红莲形态…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟然是超·秘传忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可恶 你们这群臭丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟然敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道元要逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么能让他逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要追了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女和半藏的学生竟然联手了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看来大道寺说得没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做的这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都没有意义 是错的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛 你好像搞错了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的学生之所以会变强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}并不是因为我的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她们变强是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她们为同伴着想的心在不断成长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当友人真正为友人着想的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那羁绊无法估量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的学生也做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}铃音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是半藏的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在小孩子争吵的时候大人还挤进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能容忍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟然会到这步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还有对策
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你竟然启动了自爆装置！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这下大家都完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你疯了么 道元
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这天守阁里还有别的学生在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}埋葬这一切也是我身为校主的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去救学生们吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里的构造非常的复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们会碍手碍脚的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还是快溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在就相信她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管如何她们也是死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果不想让被施在你学生身上的桎梏之术发动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}流言当真！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你果然给学生们施了邪法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道元给全部学生都施加了法术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以保守秘密的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里不久就要崩毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可没时间给你们犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卑鄙小人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要做什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真正的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既不是善亦不是恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这件事竟然是由她们来教会我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}教师 失格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛学姉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再见了 我的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟 升段考试合格啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.61,0:22:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恭喜你 飞鸟同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}庆祝庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以说了不要这种庆祝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真好呢 小飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这下就和柳生一样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被你这么一说反倒高兴不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做得很好 飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这下总算升到跟柳生一样的段位了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老师也这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管怎样说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}考得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然飞鸟也顺利升段了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家也要更加勤奋修行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本部发来了对蛇女学园的调查报告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然仔细搜查了火灾后的废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:23:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但却找不到学生的踪影
